## Cara Menjalankan
# 1. Clone repository
git clone 
# 2. Setup infrastruktur (Minggu 2)
cd infra/ && terraform init && terraform plan && terraform apply
# 3. Deploy Lambda (Minggu 3)
cd lambda/ && pip install -r requirements.txt && ./deploy.sh
